casebody.data:
LITTLE SISTERS OF THE POOR SAINTS PETER AND PAUL HOME, Petitioner
v.
PENNSYLVANIA, et al. No. 19-431 Supreme Court of the United States. January 17, 2020

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted. The case is consolidated, and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
